
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Hello, World!</title>
  </head>

  <body>
    <h1 class="title">HTML Text Formatting Examples</h1>

    <ul>
      <li><h2><b>Bold Example: Important Notice!</b></h2></li>
      <li><h3><strong>Strong Example: Warning! Save your work.</strong></h3></li>
      <li><h2><i>Italic Example: This is a book title.</i></h2></li>
      <li><h3><em>Emphasized Example: Please read carefully.</em></h3></li>
      <li><h2><mark>Mark Example: Highlighted keyword</mark></h2></li>
      <li><h2><small>Small Example: Terms and conditions apply.</small></h2></li>
      <li><h2><del>Deleted Example: Old Price ₹500</del></h2></li>
      <li><h2><ins>Inserted Example: New Price ₹300</ins></h2></li>
      <li><h2>Chemistry Example: H<sub>2</sub>O is water</h2></li>
      <li><h2>Math Example: X<sup>2</sup> + Y<sup>2</sup></h2></li>
    </ul>

  </body>
</html>
